    "name": "Voice of Chernobyl",
    "steam_appid": 1886120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886120/extras/3ad572eb387e51ea21cdcd01b8fc4fa5.avif?t=1767480496\" width=900 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Voice of Chernobyl</strong> is a Multiplayer First-Person Shooter based in the Eastern European world where you try to survive and fight for either peace or stand first place victorious</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>IF YOU'RE STILL NOT SOLD ON THIS GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Then listen to what people who've tried this game think and honestly say about it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>&quot;What do you think of Voice of Chernobyl?&quot;</i>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886120/extras/5a7f6b65c7045b043dec8169c9a8fe13.avif?t=1767480496\" width=128 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>&quot;This game is pretty dope so far! Really fun with friends and family, ha-ha!&quot; </strong><i>- Paul</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886120/extras/828918c6304f6500ca5fb09a4984ad4c.avif?t=1767480496\" width=128 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>&quot;If sexual and psychological horror were combined into one thing.&quot; </strong><i>- Also Paul, after a month</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886120/extras/f28986416084bb6b18c94fe75bce28af.avif?t=1767480496\" width=900 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>BIZARRE AND DISTINCTIVE ADVENTURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each session can vary in all sorts of ways, you're given the capability to use interesting choices of weapons in various ways, and communicate against other people or to fend off certain beings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>UNIQUE GAMEMODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Some lit gamemodes, like Survival <strong>|</strong> Deathmatch <strong>|</strong> Team Deathmatch <strong>|</strong> Melee Fight <strong>|</strong> Arms Race <strong>|</strong> Infection. They each contain their own interesting maps <i>(each game mode requires at least 2 players to play</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>NO MICROTRANSACTIONS </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Completely free - Do you need new weapons? Then just play the game as you earn certain points for free to acquire new weaponry to dominate and be the nemesis of your enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>FREE CUSTOMIZABLE CHARACTERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Make your self indistinguishable from others by just playing the game! You do not need to pay anything at all, earn free presents when a round ends, open them for free, earning you a random type of clothing with a random effect or colour. Make your own personal character to be unique from others!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>WORKSHOP MODDING SUPPORT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Of course you're given the ability to mod! Try out add-ons that can replace existing content to make it different, or that are in addition to the base game so you can play with whatever you want, your creation is your limit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>NO NEED FOR DLSS, RTX OR ANY 'FRAME GENERATION'</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Don't worry! The game has been optimized to the point where you can run it on 13+ year old laptops. You don't need DLSS, RTX or any fake frame technology, the options include settings that modify the look of the game to run on any device that should be able to run Steam</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>AND A LOT MORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Such as experimental 64 player servers (your pc might blow up though), the gibbing system on enemies, and more (<i>like a helicopter you can crash if you want or an apple juice).</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Download now and play for free!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>*Made with love &lt;3*</i></p>",
